Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Top of the building: Excellent Era]\NCaptain Liu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw Cui Li, I tried asking about it discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't reply though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if Xiao Shiqin is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,your position as the Vice-Captain might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Liu!{Was a period, but I suspect using person's name as appellative requires the exclamation mark --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my background.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, everyone in Excellent Era
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is just a country bumpkin from Thunderclap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he try to snatch the Vice-Captain seat from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, speaking of it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he does have some skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team's results been pretty poor lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Xiao Shiqin didn't join us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us all{inclusive we, tee hee --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,have a little face-to-face with that Xiao Shiqin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The club has an announcement for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin is joining us, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of the deal, you'll be sent over to Thunderclap.{"exchanged", but I can't really fit that into the sentence -- Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have three days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to pack your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You may {consequently, but most often it is not translated --Lynx}leave on Monday, July 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've used me and now you are kicking me out?{idiom: "to cross the river and tear down the bridge" --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the club is dumping me after having used me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the club use you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,could you have kicked Ye Qiu out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to report to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The club will surely deny this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that make me the scapegoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an exchange of members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we cancel the deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Termination of Contract]\Ndo you want to break your contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to retire as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll terminate the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Excellent Era]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The media is arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your contribution to the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Welcome, Xiao Shiqin]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they think I can't do anything about it if I'm made to take the side door?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it close to your heart.{lit. count, consider --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't take it close to your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look this way, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellent Era's Vice-Captain is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,TLC,[Excellent Era C{lub, first characetr of 俱乐部}]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's red light now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow the traffic rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop when the traffic light is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Excellent Era]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The light is green now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you may cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Hao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fans still saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How that's him all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had known earlier, I'd have steered clear of Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the club has something important happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even allowed to sleep in a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as chill as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin! Xiao Shiqin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Xiao Shiqin's transfer related to you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Vice-Captain of Excellent Era,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcome high-level players to join Excellent Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To this end,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you even exchanged yourself for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Su Mucheng tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you plan to leave Excellent Era since the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little unlucky now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I still get to participate in the professional matches next season.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your luck is getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in Excellent Era,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't get to join any matches next season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent Era wants to make a comeback through the Challenge Round,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but regrettably,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the slot belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You still are really full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually want to see who of you will get eliminated in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be even more entertaining if both teams go down together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you'll be disappointed, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Excellent Era's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pestering him, Wei Chen{"Old Wei" --Lynx}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rushing to take Bus Route 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and board the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Wei Chen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,his name is pronounced as Hao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that we are acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bao.{"Bun" --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it pronounced as Hao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that it's not Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we taking the Bus Route 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin! Xiao Shiqin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's indeed big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The new week's world boss fights are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin! Xiao Shiqin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[League Weekly]\NNext, we'll continue to report for you the changes of teams' rosters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[League Weekly]\NPlease, stay tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yifan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yingjie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not part of in Tiny Herb's future plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to go to an Internet cafe.{Was cybercafe, but I checked the wiki, it's referred to as the Happy Internet Cafe --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to give up, aren't you, Yifan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue training
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and improve my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,by then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we might no longer be teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll still be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Excellent Era]\NFrom today onwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will be joining Excellent Era as the Vice-Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand with us through thick and thin.{lit.: advance and retreat}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,TLC,Let's strive for the Revival Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mucheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting like Zhou Zekai today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the old players from the golden generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the vibe of a powerhouse team?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin, Sun Xiang,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,please stay, we'll go somewhere afterwards{was -- "I'll bring you to somewhere later", literal --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,TLC,[Happy Internet Cafe]{Not sure about timestamps of this and the next line --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your training room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ye Qiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,TLC,This is Shiqin.{Maybe you can think of something, Ye Xiu here is being Ye Xiu and calls Xiao Shiqin xiao3 xiao4, little Xiao, and the repetition of xiao adds another level of comedy --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Shiqin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Wei Chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The former captain of Blue Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei Chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you didn't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You were still playing with mud back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Captain Wei Chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for the rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met before, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tao Xuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO of Excellent Era, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When is Excellent Era disbanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should it be disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's knocked out, of course it's going to be disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shiqin, right?{xiao3 xiao4 again --Lynx}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you so foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent Era is going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, you hopped on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the end of the world is not coming fast enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm up against Excellent Era during the Challenge Round,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go easy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if Excellent Era gets to be our opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,telling you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just bringing our Captain and Vice-Captain to visit their seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you have any advice for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a friendly match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we're playing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we need to have a match now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll eventually meet during the league.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to greet the seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is also looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his name is Qiao Yifan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yifan is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's considered your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei Chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Soft Mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You met each other online.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,our boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chen Guo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your accommodation is arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Wei Chen and Bao will bring you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior Xiao Shiqin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior Sun Xiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really Sun Xiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really Xiao Shiqin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun Xiang and Xiao Shiqin are at Happy Internet cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they would take advantage and leave without paying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I cause trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if the glasses are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they be alright?{Won't people be damaged?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go across the road to get security from Excellent Era?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cui Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask for help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop squeezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Happy Internet Cafe]\NWe're at Happy!
